@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071/api

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Unsplash Image API
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Search for images (Default: technology)
GET {{baseUrl}}/images?query=technology HTTP/1.1

### Search for 'crypto' images
GET {{baseUrl}}/images?query=crypto&per_page=5&orientation=landscape HTTP/1.1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 2. Financial Modeling Prep (Stocks)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Stock Quote (Apple)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks?symbol=AAPL&type=quote HTTP/1.1

### Get Company Profile (Tesla)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks?symbol=TSLA&type=profile HTTP/1.1

### Search for a stock
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks?query=Microsoft&type=search HTTP/1.1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 3. Twilio Social API
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Send Invite (Requires Twilio Config)
POST {{baseUrl}}/social HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "invite",
    "to": "+1234567890",
    "message": "Hey! Check out HomeBase 2.0. It's awesome."
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 4. Existing Crypto API (CoinGecko)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Crypto Prices
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto?ids=bitcoin,ethereum,solana HTTP/1.1
